window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The wildfire isn’t the only thing burning out of control…</b><br> <br> I thought sneaking past the barricades to track my rogue sister in the wilderness was my biggest challenge but I had no idea what I was getting into. Turns out, my sister isn’t just rogue. She’s tangled up with a group that is steeped in conspiracy, with ties to dark magic and forbidden relics that could unravel the balance between shifters and humans.<br> <br> And members of my pack knew about it.</p> <p>I have no choice but to stay with a group of wildland firefighters. Getting close to humans near a blood moon is dangerous enough, but hiding out with Conner, a seasoned firefighter with sharp instincts, is reckless. There’s a spark between us that feels more than human, and every moment with him makes it harder to remember why I should keep my distance.</p> <p>But the rules are clear—shifters don’t bond with humans. And we <i>never</i> take them as mates.</p> <p>The problem is, Conner isn’t just any human. My wolf is convinced we're fated.</p> <p>But Conner has no idea what I am.</p> <p>I need to deprogram my sister and get out of here. But the bond between me and Conner isn’t one I can easily ignore, and every second we stay together only pulls me further into the fire…</p> <p><b>Buy now and start listening if you love:</b></p> <ul> <li>Forbidden Love</li> <li>Forced Proximity</li> <li>Sloooow Burn</li> <li>Firefighter Vibes</li> <li>I Have a Secret</li> </ul> <p>The third book in the Shadow Pack Series contains a HEA for Lana and Destin. The story arc spans multiple books, but each one contains a new couple and a new romance, all connected, with all the familiar faces from previous books until we discover the truth of the legends and unite the Shadow Pack once and for all.</p>"; 
